These are described in Table 1 [see 
                                 Drug Interactions (7)
                              ].

Proton Pump Inhibitors: Avoid concomitant use [see 
      Drug Interactions (7)
   ].

H2-Receptor Antagonists: Take CALQUENCE 2 hours before taking a H2-receptor antagonist [see 
      Drug Interactions (7)
   ].

Antacids: Separate dosing by at least 2 hours [see 
                                 Drug Interactions (7)
                              ].

